communityAlerts.title: 2 FEG-Related Flashloan Exploits
communityAlerts.desc: On May-15-2022 08:22:49 PM +UTC and On May-16-2022 11:31:29 +UTC FEG and their related tokens and projects experienced separate flashloan incidents. They lost ~$1.3M on the 15th and ~$1.9M on the 16th. The incidents were caused by errors w/ a flaw in the “swapToSwap()” function that was leveraged via flashloan attack.
